description:
What type of enforcement is coming to America soon? Join Truth Matters with hosts MacKenzie Drebit and Matthew Schanche for a deep dive into the prophetic implications for America. In this episode, we explore the alignment of recent political actions with biblical predictions, the rise of the false prophet, and the potential for history to repeat itself. Discover how religious and political powers may converge, and the significance of Project 2025 in shaping future religious enforcement. Don't miss out on this eye-opening exploration of real-world evidence supporting Bible prophecy!
